            <title><![CDATA[#中国医师节# 【看病找他们！深圳公布40名“好医生”，我连夜打印贴床头[求饶][666]】目前全深圳共有6.77万名医生，“医”海茫茫，你让我推荐哪个好？就在8月17...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BB%E5%B8%88%E8%8A%82%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#中国医师节#</span></a> 【看病找他们！深圳公布40名“好医生”，我连夜打印贴床头<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】目前全深圳共有6.77万名医生，“医”海茫茫，你让我推荐哪个好？就在8月17号晚，因为“8·19”中国医师节来了，深圳举办了一场庆祝大会！小卫一口气拿到了两份靠谱名单，好家伙，一共40个了不起的深圳医生<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>今天，我就把这40个大神，一次过“泄露”给家人们，近期要看病的朋友，记得赶紧保存、收藏👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E7%9A%84%E7%9E%AC%E9%97%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E7%9A%84%E7%9E%AC%E9%97%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#被医生治愈的瞬间#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E7%B2%BE%E8%AF%9A%E5%8C%BB%E8%80%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E7%B2%BE%E8%AF%9A%E5%8C%BB%E8%80%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#守护精诚医者#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpt2yddg20rs0gkqhc.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpdfk4tj20zk3wu7j0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpe2j4cj20zk22nn4r.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpej7osj20zk22ogtt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpf6a8oj20v95is1eu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpfv2pmj20v94k2nku.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpgimhkj20v95fyx18.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vph235bj20v95xpha9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vphoruej20v951twvh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpibex1j20v95xme3u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0vpcjey7j20v94oynhj.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
