        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【要说多少句对不起，才能成长为一个好医生？】 医院的墙，比教堂听过更多虔诚的祈祷，进了医者这道门，生、老、病、死，躲都躲不掉，“拜托你了，一定要帮我们...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【要说多少句对不起，才能成长为一个好医生？】 医院的墙，比教堂听过更多虔诚的祈祷，进了医者这道门，生、老、病、死，躲都躲不掉，“拜托你了，一定要帮我们想想办法” “你这样算什么医生！”……他们拼尽全力，有时却也无能为力。从疼痛、失败、死亡里不断站起来重新出发，去治愈伤、去追逐光，是每一个医生成长的必经之路<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[微风]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_weifeng-6dce9bef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>有时治愈，常常帮助，总是安慰，嗨，8月19日是你的节日，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%8C%BB%E5%B8%88%E8%8A%82%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#中国医师节#</span></a>。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E7%9A%84%E7%9E%AC%E9%97%B4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%A2%AB%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%B2%BB%E6%84%88%E7%9A%84%E7%9E%AC%E9%97%B4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#被医生治愈的瞬间#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E7%B2%BE%E8%AF%9A%E5%8C%BB%E8%80%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E7%B2%BE%E8%AF%9A%E5%8C%BB%E8%80%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#守护精诚医者#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4936034291744771" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hh0rk05mx9j21hc0u07e7.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/c5W3p8xWgx087TJVqZLO01041201b8fU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1692430030&amp;ssig=dI5tNpRoAO&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/LddM6UHjgx087TJUBTTa01041200BaLQ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x