            <description><![CDATA[【今天全国护发日，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B6%85%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E9%98%B2%E7%A7%83%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B6%85%E5%AE%9E%E7%94%A8%E9%98%B2%E7%A7%83%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#超实用防秃攻略#</span></a>来了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】①正常发际线通常为眉上4指宽；②熬夜、过量饮酒、频繁烫染、压力大为<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人脱发的四大原因#</span></a>；③盲目用生姜黑芝麻丸或加重脱发…“头顶大事”，一起get👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> （人民日报） <img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0ny91rpej20go0l3q5x.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0ny9id8tj20go0gpwgr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0ny9ynuyj20go0mewi7.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0nyaar9fj20go0nnn0k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0nyal02fj20go0n3dj1.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0nyb26m9j20go0s9dk3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hh0